          "Jenn Wolfe"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You were just a normal college student, minding your business, when the world got weird on you. Last Halloween, you and your housemates went out for a party. A few drinks, some recreational drug usage, maybe you got a little reckless with a stranger. You ended up bringing them home. The next night, you woke up thinking you had the world's worst hangover - and perhaps you did, because you figured out fairly quickly you might be a vampire. Seriously, how does this happen? And why? Who knows, the person who made you didn't stick around to explain anything to you. You've had to figure this all out from your scant research and digging around on the internet. You only found the others by mistake one night, and frankly they were a lot more scary! You've spent the last year trying to survive under the radar only to find a whole society of vampires, all of whom would gladly eat you for lunch if they could. You have powers, though, and they seem to all be geared towards investigating threats and protecting your body, so you go with your strengths.\n\nWorse, your sleeping days have been filled with these horrible dreams and visions of war and death and of destruction - but also of new things, of change, of something new rising from the ashes. You have no idea what it is all about, but you know you are a survivor. Maybe it means that despite these monsters you find yourslf among, you will survive no matter what - you hope. But as what...who knows."
        ],
